{"tid":737983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣傳片畫風被指抄襲《你的名字》　港鐵：我話ok就ok","createTime":"2018-07-11T07:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T12:24:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":170,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf2325a199f7c4c1bebb42d717b040992c57e49","tid":737983,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180711/s00001/1531292026907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180711%2Fs00001%2F1531292026907&d=ePjZ8s8nzOd0IjjNpBSjj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dfc327ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180711%2Fs00001%2F1531292026907&h=d4c17689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180711/s00001/1531292026907</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180711/s00001/50b26b3ad741f6c20c88ac6b5cd0b34c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180711%2Fs00001%2F50b26b3ad741f6c20c88ac6b5cd0b34c.jpg&h=ae17fedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩年前，日本漫畫電影作品《你的名字》叫好又叫座，作者新海誠的畫風，至今仍廣為人知。近日，港鐵推出一段題為《港鐵上的他和她》的漫畫宣傳片後，惹起網民熱議，甚至有人指控有關作品是抄襲《你的名字》。港鐵回應本報查詢時強調，有關作品有其獨特性。<br />\n<br />\n片段上星期二（3日）起上載於港鐵facebook專頁，並於本周起開始在網上熱傳，截至今日3時左右，已累積21萬人次瀏覽，並有2100多個分享。片段中，港鐵以漫畫風格描繪多個香港場景，包括港鐵車廂、九龍灣港鐵總部、牛頭角站出口，和調景嶺站月台等。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，有關片段沒有反映如車廂擁擠、訊號故障，和票價高昂等現實，又斥責有關片段畫風與《你的名字》十分相似，甚至指控港鐵抄襲。不過，亦有網民讚揚片段所繪背景漂亮，站在廣告角度來說題材亦比較新穎，坦言畫風相似不等於抄襲。另外，也有專頁二次創作，以自製字幕配上《你的名字》原聲，諷刺港鐵屢屢加價且經常故障。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回應本報查詢時表示，有關作品是伙拍本地公司，以實景動漫風格製作，目的在於宣傳乘車安全及禮讓文化，強調富有其獨特性。"},{"pid":"6a482a0227f47c35adf5a454a0e9343d362ed6e9","tid":737983,"uid":191815,"like":107,"dislike":2,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"又比日本仔笑一国二制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb0d18f3304c0b4973f5a907864c77ab7d116b0","tid":737983,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db30039e477fc06498fcbb27b81ec46acc91fd7","tid":737983,"uid":29314,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"仲要抄前年既野。<br />\n<br />\n好心抄得update d啦"},{"pid":"e5a6b0c91da266cbdc71683316c568b2966e9115","tid":737983,"uid":29063,"like":140,"dislike":2,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L_LtIBTAooQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL_LtIBTAooQ&d=ePjZ8s8nzOd0IjjNpBSjj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=81d89e53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L_LtIBTAooQ</a>"},{"pid":"0d96f73921b90a9b7359454d7929f12efed0de59","tid":737983,"uid":108347,"like":24,"dislike":89,"score":-65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"點分referencing 同抄? 好多宣傳片特登用名作啲經典位，唔通男係女後面，女張開手就全部係抄鐵達尼?呢單野狗鐵都係抽下水姐，佢似係想你一睇就知係你的名字wo"},{"pid":"6d3e5db711529da343c2b44aba464e1432bf0742","tid":737983,"uid":2442,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"係咪大陸公司做？"},{"pid":"b7f84122e3322d12f729ea79321eb9cc7106a583","tid":737983,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a014fa69994f657da5c47130cded57a6fbf12010","tid":737983,"uid":77196,"like":70,"dislike":5,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"0d96f73921b90a9b7359454d7929f12efed0de59","tid":737983,"uid":108347,"like":24,"dislike":89,"score":-65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"點分referencing 同抄? 好多宣傳片特登用名作啲經典位，唔通男係女後面，女張開手就全部係抄鐵達尼?呢單野狗鐵都係抽下水姐，佢似係想你一睇就知係你的名字wo"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"一睇就諗到你的名字，已經係侵犯版